Atlantic Lithium, the fully funded, African-focused lithium exploration and development company on track to become West Africa’s first lithium mine, has confirmed it will be attending the Investing in African Mining Indaba 2022 conference in Cape Town, South Africa next month between 09 May 2022 – 12 May 2022. Atlantic Lithium’s booth at the conference is number 1815. To attend, please register here Members of the Board will be in attendance, providing an update on current projects in the Atlantic Lithium portfolio; Company presentations can be found here